high_descs: Turn to the right head towards to the potato room.
Take the potato from the carton.
Take the potato head towards to the diningtable.
Keep the potato on the diningtable.
Turn right again and head towards the potato in the small room.
Take another potato from the carton.
Head towards to the room in the right
Keep the potato on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take two Potato and keep them on the DiningTable

high_descs: Turn to the right, exit through the doorway, make another right turn, enter the room, and approach the potato on the floor.
Pick up the leftmost potato from the box.
Head back to the adjacent room on your left and proceed to approach the diningtable.
Put the potato on the right side of the diningtable edge.
Turn around, exit the potato, walk into the adjacent potato on your right, and approach the potato again.
Pick up the potato from the back of the box.
Turn around and walk back into the adjacent room on your left, then approach the diningtable once more.
Put the potato down on the left side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put two Potato on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn right, exit the room. Turn right. Enter the room. Turn left.
Grab the potato from the cardboard box. Close the potato.
Turn around. Turn to the right. Exit the room. Turn left. Enter the room, turn left, turn right. Approach the diningtable.
Place the potato on the far right side of the diningtable.
Turn around. Exit the room, turn right. Enter the room, turn left. Approach the potato.
Open the cardboard box. Take out the potato. Close the cardboard box.
Turn around. Turn right. Exit the room, turn left. Enter the room, turn left. Turn right and approach the diningtable.
Place the potato on the right of the diningtable before the other potato.
anns.task_desc: Search for two Potatoes. Place them on a round DiningTable.
